                    <div class="exc-description">
                        <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Perfecting weighted pull-ups boosts power, strength, and endurance, enhancing performance in other exercises for optimal training success. This is your master guide from start to finish to get you there. </span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We will take you through how to do it, provide you with expert tips, and give you the perfect sets, and reps markers to work from. We’ll also help you on how to start programming them into your workout. </span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Let’s take a look at the weighted pull-up in more detail below.</span></p>                    </div>
